'''白枕鶴'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Antigone vipio''）是[[鶴科|鶴科]][[赤頸鶴屬|赤頸鶴屬]]的成員之一，身高大約130厘米，體重大約5.6[[公斤|公斤]]。牠們的腳是粉紅色的，頸部條灰白兩間，前灰後白，面部紅色。白枕鹤全球种群数量为3700-4500只<ref>{{cite web |title=Antigone vipio |url=http://datazone.birdlife.org/species/factsheet/white-naped-crane-antigone-vipio |website=BirdLife International |accessdate=2021-01-13 |archive-date=2020-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200204075725/http://datazone.birdlife.org/species/factsheet/white-naped-crane-antigone-vipio |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==分布==
白枕鶴主要分为东、西两个种群。东部种群在中俄交界处的[[黑龙江|黑龙江]]流域、[[三江平原|三江平原]]和[[松嫩平原|松嫩平原]]繁殖, 迁徙经过[[朝鲜半岛|朝鲜半岛]], 在[[朝韩非军事区|朝韩非军事区]]和[[日本|日本]][[九州岛|九州岛]][[出水市|出水市]]越冬；西部种群在中蒙俄交界处的[[达乌尔|达乌尔]]地区繁殖, 迁徙途径[[渤海湾|渤海湾]]、[[华北平原|华北平原]], 在[[长江|长江]]中下游地区越冬。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Lang |first1=Xuemin |last2=Purev-Ochir |first2=Gankhuyag |last3=Terbish |first3=Oyunchimeg |last4=Khurelbaatar |first4=Dashdorj |last5=Erdenechimeg |first5=Baasansuren |last6=Gungaa |first6=Amarkhuu |last7=Mi |first7=Chunrong |last8=Guo |first8=Yumin |title=Luan River upper reaches: The important stopover site of the white-naped crane (Grus vipio) western population |journal=Biodiversity Science |date=2020-10-20 |volume=28 |issue=10 |pages=1213 |doi=10.17520/biods.2020100}}</ref>

==分类学==
在之前的分类中，白枕鹤属于[[鹤属|鹤属]]。但2010年发表的一项[[分子系统发生学|分子系统发生学]]研究表明，鹤属是[[多系群|多系群]]的。<ref>{{cite journal | last1=Krajewski | first1=C. | last2=Sipiorski | first2=J.T. | last3=Anderson | first3=F.E. | year=2010 | title=Mitochondrial genome sequences and the phylogeny of cranes (Gruiformes:  Gruidae) | journal=Auk | volume=127 | issue=2 | pages=440–452 | doi=10.1525/auk.2009.09045 | url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/277486138_Complete_Mitochondrial_Genome_Sequences_and_the_Phylogeny_of_Cranes_Gruiformes_Gruidae | access-date=2018-11-25 | archive-date=2019-05-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190519055349/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/277486138_Complete_Mitochondrial_Genome_Sequences_and_the_Phylogeny_of_Cranes_Gruiformes_Gruidae | dead-url=no }}</ref>所以，在之后对鹤科重新分类中，白枕鹤、[[沙丘鹤|沙丘鹤]]、[[赤颈鹤|赤颈鹤]]和[[澳洲鹤|澳洲鹤]]被移到了[[赤颈鹤属|赤颈鹤属]]。赤颈鹤属这一分类最早由[[德国|德国]]鸟类学家[[路德維希·賴興巴赫|路德維希·賴興巴赫]]于1853年提出。<ref name=ioc>{{cite web | editor1-last=Gill | editor1-first=Frank | editor2-last=Donsker | editor2-first=David | year=2017 | title=Rails, gallinules, trumpeters & cranes | work=World Bird List Version 7.2 | url=http://www.worldbirdnames.org/bow/rails/ | publisher=International Ornithologists' Union | accessdate=2017-06-28 | archive-date=2014-05-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140506040300/http://www.worldbirdnames.org/bow/rails/ | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | last=Reichenbach | first=Ludwig | author-link=路德維希·賴興巴赫 | year=1853 | title=Reichenbach Handbuch der speciellen Ornithologie | publisher=Friedrich Hofmeister | place=Leipzig | page=xxiii | url=https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/47618653 | access-date=2018-11-25 | archive-date=2018-12-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181201135438/https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/47618653 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

